<div>

<div class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen font-sans text-slate-900 antialiased selection:bg-indigo-100">

  <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-20 px-6">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-6xl">
      Hi, I'm <span class="text-indigo-600">Alex Chen</span>.
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I am a software engineer focused on building clean, performant, and accessible web applications. I enjoy solving complex architectural problems and turning them into simple, beautiful digital experiences.
      </p>
      <p>
        When I'm not coding, you'll usually find me exploring abstract algebra or deep-diving into group theory. I'm particularly fascinated by how structures like the group $G = C_5 \times C_5 \times C_4$ provide elegant counterexamples in mathematical proofs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-20 px-6">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold border-b border-slate-200 pb-4 mb-10">Portfolio Projects</h2>

    <div class="grid gap-8">

      <article class="group relative flex flex-col items-start p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 transition hover:shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          <span class="absolute -inset-x-4 -inset-y-6 z-0 scale-95 bg-slate-50 opacity-0 transition group-hover:scale-100 group-hover:opacity-100 sm:-inset-x-6 sm:rounded-2xl"></span>
          <span class="relative z-10 text-indigo-600">Sylow Calculator</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="relative z-10 mt-2 text-slate-600">
          A visualization tool for finite groups that helps identify Sylow p-subgroups and verifies properties of group orders.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/user/sylow-calc" class="relative z-10 mt-4 flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 hover:text-indigo-500">
          View on GitHub
        </a>
      </article>

      <article class="group relative flex flex-col items-start p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 transition hover:shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          <span class="absolute -inset-x-4 -inset-y-6 z-0 scale-95 bg-slate-50 opacity-0 transition group-hover:scale-100 group-hover:opacity-100 sm:-inset-x-6 sm:rounded-2xl"></span>
          <span class="relative z-10 text-indigo-600">Tailwind Component Library</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="relative z-10 mt-2 text-slate-600">
          A collection of accessible, copy-paste components built with Tailwind CSS and Headless UI.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/user/tailwind-lib" class="relative z-10 mt-4 flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 hover:text-indigo-500">
          View on GitHub
        </a>
      </article>

    </div>
  </main>

</div>



